Animal Farm.name: Animal Farm
Animal Farm.description: +1% Total Damage for every different species you have bred within Pet Breeding. You just need to breed the pet type one time for it to count! @ - @ Total Bonus: {%

Wired In.name: Wired In
Wired In.description: All Uploaded Players print 2x more resources from their section of the 3D Printer. The displayed amount will NOT appear doubled, just to avoid confusion as to what your actual base Sampling Rate is, but it will be displayed in blue.

Gilded Cyclical Tubing.name: Gilded Cyclical Tubing
Gilded Cyclical Tubing.description: All refinery cycles occur 3x faster. Faster cycles means more salts!

No Bubble Left Behind.name: No Bubble Left Behind
No Bubble Left Behind.description: Every 24 hours, your 3 lowest level Alchemy Bubbles gets +1 Lv. This only applies to bubbles Lv 5 or higher, so it's more like 'your lowest level bubble that is at least level 5'

Killer's Brightside.name: Killer's Brightside
Killer's Brightside.description: All monster kills count for 2x more than normal for things like opening portals and Death Note. Doesn't increase resource drops or exp gain.

Shrine World Tour.name: Shrine World Tour
Shrine World Tour.description: If a shrine is placed within town, instead of in a monster map, it will act as though it is placed in EVERY map in that entire world!

Viaduct of the Gods.name: Viaduct of the Gods
Viaduct of the Gods.description: All alchemy liquids have x5 higher max capacity. However, you regenerate alchemy liquids -30% slower.

Certified Stamp Book.name: Certified Stamp Book
Certified Stamp Book.description: All Stamps, except for MISC tab stamps, give DOUBLE the bonus.

Spelunker Obol.name: Spelunker Obol
Spelunker Obol.description: 1.50x higher effects from all active Jewels within the Mainframe.

Fungi Finger Pocketer.name: Fungi Finger Pocketer
Fungi Finger Pocketer.description: +2% extra cash from monsters for every 1 million Green Mushroom kills your account has, which can be viewed at Death Note. @ - @ Total Bonus: {%

My 1st Chemistry Set.name: My 1st Chemistry Set
My 1st Chemistry Set.description: All Vials in Alchemy give DOUBLE the bonus. The bonus description will reflect this doubling.

Unadulterated Banking Fury.name: Unadulterated Banking Fury
Unadulterated Banking Fury.description: +2% Total Damage for each 'greened' stack of resources in your bank. A 'greened' stack is one with 10 million or more items. @ - @ Total Bonus: {%
